Package: rogueportal
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, bridge-utils, dnsmasq, iptables-persistent, macchanger, nginx
Description: Rogue Portal
 A configuration package that configures a system as a rogue captive portal.

Package: roguefastboot
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Rogue Portal Fast Boot
 A configuration package that configures a system to boot faster for a rogue
 captive portal by disabling unneeded services.
